list.name: Changes
list.comment: - Initialised new project - 'Good reader' - Imported recommended package such as: - 'Time' module for letting the screen wait before hard shutting down the web-page. - 'Selenium4' module for accessing webdriver as well as chrome service web scrapping. - Added url for required webpage - Acquired target element in webpage 'Book Category' - Formatted the category titles, and it's links to a dictionary as a Dictionary comprehensive fashion by removing unwanted dummy links through dictionary comprehension condition. - Project successful.
